    "Title": "Overdrive Initiative: XENOTHREAT SURVEILLANCE",
    "Description": "One of the suspects captured during the recent attacks revealed that XenoThreat is looking to remotely access a number of comm arrays around the system.\n\nHaving XenoThreat listening into comms is extremely dangerous for the people living here, so the CDF has been enlisted to reset the comm array, then defend it from any XenoThreat Vanguards that will attempt to reconnect to the servers. \n\nOnce those Vanguards have been defeated, clear out any remaining hostile ships in the area.\n\nAs a reminder, the military has generously donated some old F7A Hornets for CDF members who see this initiative through to the end.",
